Telamont, during his time as the arcanist Shadow, was noted for creating a number of spells centered around [[shadow magic]]. They follow here with the year the spells were created:
*''[[shadow door|Shadow's door]]'' in {{Yearlink|-600}}
*''[[shades|Shadow's shades]]'' in {{Yearlink|-597}}
*''[[demishadow magic|Shadow's demimagic]]'' in {{Yearlink|-594}}
*''[[summon shadow|Shadow's summons]]'' in {{Yearlink|-594}}
*''[[Shadow evocation|Shadow's magic]]'' in {{Yearlink|-593}}
*''[[shadow walk|Shadow's walk]]'' in {{Yearlink|-592}}
*''[[shadow monsters|Shadow's monster]]'' in {{Yearlink|-588}}
*''[[demishadow monster|Shadow's demimonster]]'' in {{Yearlink|-587}}
